choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for this week.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Here is your healthy meal plan for the next seven days:

Breakfast:
- Oatmeal with banana and berries (no milk)
Lunch:
- Quinoa salad with avocado, tomatoes, cucumber, red onion, lemon juice, olive oil, salt & pepper (no cheese or garlic)
Dinner:
- Baked chicken breast over roasted vegetables (broccoli, cauliflower, carrots) with a side of brown rice and steamed green beans
Snacks:
- Apple slices with almond butter (no pistachios or cashews)
- Celery sticks with hummus
- Edamame (soybeans)
- Fresh fruit salad (no honey)

Make sure to drink plenty of water throughout the day and get adequate sleep.  Good luck!
